{"title":"Votec VRX affordable alloy gravel bike is back with off-road updates","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/11/15/votec-vrx-affordable-alloy-gravel-bike-is-back-with-off-road-updates/","date":1637000281000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130537/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_blur.jpg\" data-fancybox=\"\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130537/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_blur-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Votec VRX affordable alloy GRX fast gravel bike updated, photo by Felix Reimers,&nbsp;blur\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130537/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_blur-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130537/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_blur-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130537/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_blur-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130537/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_blur-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130537/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_blur-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130537/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_blur.jpg 2000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></a><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></div><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-278375\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>Originally launched back in 2016, Stuttgart’s Votec bikes are back with a revamped version of their popular affordable alloy VRX gravel bike. With an all-new carbon fork, updated aluminum frame, and bigger tire clearance all around, the new VRX is a more capable gravel bike than ever, without breaking the bank… in stock now!</p><h2>Votec VRX affordable alloy fast gravel bike</h2><div id=\"attachment_278446\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130533/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_adventure-bike.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-278446\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130533/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_adventure-bike.jpg\" alt=\"Votec VRX affordable alloy GRX fast gravel bike updated, photo by Felix Reimers,&nbsp;forest adventure\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1500\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130533/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_adventure-bike.jpg 2000w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130533/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_adventure-bike-297x223.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130533/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_adventure-bike-800x600.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130533/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_adventure-bike-120x90.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130533/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_adventure-bike-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130533/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_adventure-bike-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-278446\">c. Votec, photos by Felix Reimers,</p></div><p>When Votec launched their carbon <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/09/30/review-votec-vrc-all-road-bike-finds-happy-medium-versatility-between-road-gravel/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">VRC endurance road</a> bike last summer, it blurred the lines between all-road and fast gravel a bit with 35mm tire clearance. You see, as gravel keeps getting broken down into subcategories based on tire size, Votec feels like gravel tires “between 35-42mm represent the sweet spot: the perfect compromise between weight, grip, and cushioning” for mixed-surface riding. The <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2016/04/07/vote-vrx-gravel-road-bike-spins-production/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">original alloy VRX</a> topped out at 40mm, but this new bike ratchets tire clearance up to 700x42mm.</p><h3>What’s new?</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130528/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_complete-yellow.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130528/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_complete-yellow.jpg\" alt=\"Votec VRX affordable alloy GRX fast gravel bike updated, complete\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130528/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_complete-yellow.jpg 2000w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130528/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_complete-yellow-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130528/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_complete-yellow-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130528/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_complete-yellow-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130528/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_complete-yellow-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130528/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_complete-yellow-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"></a></p><p>To fit bigger tires in the new VRX, Votec created an all-new wider &amp; stiffer full UD carbon fork for the updated gravel bike.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130523/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_new-fork-details.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130523/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_new-fork-details.jpg\" alt=\"Votec VRX affordable alloy GRX fast gravel bike updated, new fork detail\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1500\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130523/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_new-fork-details.jpg 2000w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130523/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_new-fork-details-297x223.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130523/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_new-fork-details-800x600.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130523/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_new-fork-details-120x90.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130523/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_new-fork-details-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130523/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_new-fork-details-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"></a></p><p>Also designed by Rafael Hoffleit who shaped the carbon all-road VRC, the new fork shares the same smooth look, with unique internal cable routing that enters a small shelf in the fork crown, just in front of the head tube.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130519/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_rear-end-details.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130519/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_rear-end-details.jpg\" alt=\"Votec VRX affordable alloy GRX fast gravel bike updated, frame details\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130519/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_rear-end-details.jpg 2000w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130519/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_rear-end-details-297x149.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130519/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_rear-end-details-800x400.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130519/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_rear-end-details-120x60.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130519/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_rear-end-details-768x384.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130519/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_rear-end-details-1536x768.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"></a></p><p>The heavily shaped, hydroformed 6061-T6 alloy frame is mostly unchanged, although it does squeeze an extra couple of millimeters out around the 1x-only chainstays to get the same 42mm clearance as the fork. The revised frame also shifts to modular internal cable routing through the front triangle, and updates cable guides along the chainstay to work better with the new Shimano GRX 1x gravel drivetrain.</p><h3>Tech details</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130516/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_forest.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130516/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_forest.jpg\" alt=\"Votec VRX affordable alloy GRX fast gravel bike updated, photo by Felix Reimers,&nbsp;forest complete\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130516/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_forest.jpg 2000w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130516/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_forest-297x178.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130516/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_forest-800x480.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130516/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_forest-120x72.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130516/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_forest-768x461.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130516/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_forest-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"></a></p><p>The updated 1x alloy gravel bike features 12mm thru-axles, neatly integrated flat mount disc brakes, a 1.125-1.5″ internal headset in the tapered headtube, a PressFit BB86 bottom bracket,&nbsp;and 27.2mm seatpost with a conventional external clamp.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130512/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_geometry.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130512/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_geometry.jpg\" alt=\"Votec VRX affordable alloy GRX fast gravel bike updated, geometry\" width=\"2000\" height=\"950\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130512/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_geometry.jpg 2000w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130512/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_geometry-297x141.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130512/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_geometry-800x380.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130512/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_geometry-120x57.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130512/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_geometry-768x365.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130512/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_geometry-1536x730.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"></a></p><p>It is available in five stock sizes (S-XXL) to fit a wide range of gravel riders, with “racy geometry” that Votec developed for fast rides over all hard surfaces. They call it “<em>a gravel bike with road bike genes</em>“.</p><h3>Votec VRX gravel bike – Pricing, options &amp; availability</h3><div id=\"attachment_278449\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130911/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_warwickshire-green-complete.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-278449\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130911/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_warwickshire-green-complete.jpg\" alt=\"Votec VRX affordable alloy GRX fast gravel bike updated, photo by Felix Reimers,&nbsp;green complete\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130911/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_warwickshire-green-complete.jpg 1800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130911/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_warwickshire-green-complete-297x165.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130911/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_warwickshire-green-complete-800x444.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130911/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_warwickshire-green-complete-120x67.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130911/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_warwickshire-green-complete-768x427.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130911/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_warwickshire-green-complete-1536x853.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-278449\">Votec VRX gravel bike in Warwickshire green</p></div><p>The updated Votec VRX alloy gravel bike is available now in just a single mixed Shimano GRX 1×11 bike build for 1999€, at a claimed 9.36kg complete.</p><div id=\"attachment_278439\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130505/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_yellow-zoom.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-278439\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130505/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_yellow-zoom.jpg\" alt=\"Votec VRX affordable alloy GRX fast gravel bike updated, photo by Felix Reimers,&nbsp;yellow frameset\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130505/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_yellow-zoom.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130505/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_yellow-zoom-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130505/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_yellow-zoom-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130505/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_yellow-zoom-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130505/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_yellow-zoom-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-278439\">Votec VRX gravel bike in Brazilian yellow</p></div><p>It combines a Shimano GRX 40T crankset with a SRAM chain &amp; 10-42T cassette for a rather unique wide-range setup, paired to 37mm WTB Riddler tires on 24mm internal tubeless-ready Easton EA70 AX wheels.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130502/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_riding-detail.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130502/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_riding-detail.jpg\" alt=\"Votec VRX affordable alloy GRX fast gravel bike updated, photo by Felix Reimers,&nbsp;riding detail\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1500\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130502/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_riding-detail.jpg 2000w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130502/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_riding-detail-297x223.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130502/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_riding-detail-800x600.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130502/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_riding-detail-120x90.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130502/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_riding-detail-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/15130502/Votec-VRX-affordable-alloy-GRX-fast-gravel-bike-updated_photo-by-Felix-Reimers_riding-detail-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"></a></p><p>The new Votec VRX is sold exclusively consumer-direct through their InternetStores sibling online shop <a href=\"https://www.bruegelmann.de/votec-vrx-heritage-M1004541.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Brügelmann</a>,&nbsp;available in matte black, Brazilian yellow, or Warwickshire green.</p><p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZgUkR6MqreU?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;start=18&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\"></iframe></p><p>What’s next? Bike rumors suggest that Votec is already working on a carbon gravel bike to follow up their VRC all-road bike. Will they call it the VRXC, VRCX, or maybe just VXC? In any case, we expect to know more sometime in the middle of next year.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.votec.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>Votec.com</em></a></p></section></article></div></div>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"e0b9bd8bba4f64e5fd823924337f6e6df120ed291144cfa1c33bc5f96ecc6fd5","category":"Cycling"}